OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,6,Frain at times, though parts of the
OL,7,Feast coast will stay dry. Some heavier
OL,8,Frain reaching Dumfries and Galloway by
OL,9,Fevening, with strong winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FHeavy rain will sweep east
OL,12,Facross the region this evening
OL,13,Faccompanied by strong to gale south or
OL,14,Fsouthwest winds. Clearer for a time
OL,15,Ftonight then blustery showers setting
OL,16,Fin.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
